_sText:
This is a gungame map I created for my server.  The setting is down in a valley and the theme was made to have a fort look.  
This is a symmetrical map for even teamplay and each home base has 3 floors that are accessible by ladders. 
The map includes a 3D skybox and there are 34 spawn points. 
There is also a nav file included. 
I'm open to all constructive criticism.
